		<div id="banner_wrap">
			<div id="banner">
			<h1 class="section_name">Call for Papers</h1>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--end banner-->
	</div>

	<div id="main">

		<div id="col1">
			<div style="text-align: center;">
	<a class="rollover_btn" href="/en/call-for-papers/speaker">Speaker Area</a>
</div>

<p>We are looking for the best speakers, willing to share their experience and their skills with developers and managers.</p>

<p>
The 2013 conference will cover the following aspects of Web development: 
</p>

<div class="columns-3 bg-block">
<ul>
	<li>.NET</li>
	<li>Accessibility</li>
	<li>API Integration</li>
	<li>Architecture</li>
	<li>Cloud</li>
	<li>Data Persistance</li>
	<li>DevOps</li>
	<li>E-Commerce</li>
	<li>Front-End</li>
	<li>Java</li>
	<li>JavaScript</li>
	<li>Mobile</li>
	<li>Performance</li>
	<li>PHP</li>
	<li>Project Management</li>
	<li>Python</li>
	<li>Quality Assurance</li>
	<li>Ruby</li>
	<li>Security</li>
	<li>Social Web</li>
	<li>UX</li>
	<li>Web Standards</li>
</ul>
</div>

<p>You may present in English or in French. If you can present in either language, simply add a note when submitting. Presentations are 45 minutes + 15 minutes for Q&amp;A.</p>

<h2 class="heading_h2">When and Where?</h2>

<p>ConFoo 2013 will take place at the Hilton Bonaventure Hotel in Montreal, Canada from Feb 27 to Mar  1.</p>

	<div class="media media-center">
		<img width="600" height="73" src="/images/content/2013/cfp_timeline_en.jpg" />
	</div>

<p>Subscribe to our speaker <a href="/en/newsletter/speaker/subscribe">newsletter</a> to be notified when the Call for Papers opens.</p>

<h2 class="heading_h2">Speaker's Kit</h2>

<ul class="li-spaced">	
	<li>We cover travel and accommodation expenses for speakers outside of Quebec. Typically 3 nights for North-Americans and 5 nights for more distant speakers. 
		<!-- <span class="red">Most conferences don't cover travel. Accommodation often means only 2 nights.</span> --></li>
		
	<div class="media media-frame  media-right"><img width="300" height="200" src="/images/content/2013/photo_dessert.jpg" /></div>	
	<li>We provide a continental breakfast and a hot, delicious lunch. 
		<!-- <span class="red">Many conferences don't offer lunch. Some may offer cold sandwiches or junk food.</span> --></li>
	<li>We have activities for you from the day you arrive until the day you leave: drinks, dinners and parties. 
		<!-- <span class="red">Most conferences let speakers forage for food on their own after business hours.</span> --></li>
	<li>Speakers are also invited to a private banquet with sponsors and with members of the organization committee.</li>
	<li>Speakers benefit from full access to presentations and activities for the duration of the event.</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="heading_h2">Talk Proposal</h2>

<div class="media media-frame  media-right"><img width="300" height="200" src="/images/content/2013/photo_comp.jpg" /></div>
<a class="rollover_btn small" href="/en/call-for-papers/guidelines">Proposal Guildelines</a>

<p>The selection committee will study every proposal. The decision will be made according to the originality of the proposal and to the interest from the targeted audience. Candidates will receive the decision via e-mail; decision is final and without appeal.</p>
<p>Due to hundreds of proposals, we cannot provide specific reasons for any refusal.</p>

<div class="info">
	We do not discriminate candidates based on age, gender, ethnicity, handicap or appearance. Please feel welcome to submit.
</div>
		</div>
